Index: linux-2.6/arch/x86/kernel/ptrace_bts.c
===================================================================
--- /dev/null	1970-01-01 00:00:00.000000000 +0000
+++ linux-2.6/arch/x86/kernel/ptrace_bts.c	2007-11-20 08:35:28.%N
